Package org.tribuo.impl

package org.tribuo.impl
Provides implementations of base classes and interfaces from org.tribuo.

It contains two base implementations of Example, one using primitive arrays and one using a List of Feature objects. The array implementation should be preferred for performance reasons until Feature becomes a value type. There is a subclass of ArrayExample which stores the feature indices. This is a performance optimisation and should not be used without proper consideration.
